    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13827#discussion_r3531830239\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Unfortunately <code>&lt;*const T&gt;::cast&lt;U&gt;</code> requires <code>U: Sized</code>, so I don't think we can use standard library helpers to remove <code>as</code> here :(</p>\n</blockquote>",
